Do you want to come on a walk with me?” [MASK] would shake her head. Minutes after her mother had left the house, [MASK] would miss her terribly and decide to run after her. She would run out the door of the redbrick house and down a long hill, chasing the figure in white at the end of the road. But for some reason she could never catch up with her mother.
